<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-4">SVN to GitLab Migration</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center mb-5">
      SVN 저장소를 GitLab으로 빠르고 안전하게 마이그레이션하세요.
    </p>
    
    <div class="row mb-5">
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="rounded-circle bg-primary text-white d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-cloud-upload" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.406 1.342A5.53 5.53 0 0 1 8 0c2.69 0 4.923 2 5.166 4.579C14.758 4.804 16 6.137 16 7.773 16 9.569 14.502 11 12.687 11H10a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h2.688C13.979 10 15 8.988 15 7.773c0-1.216-1.02-2.228-2.313-2.228h-.5v-.5C12.188 2.825 10.328 1 8 1a4.53 4.53 0 0 0-2.941 1.1c-.757.652-1.153 1.438-1.153 2.055v.448l-.445.049C2.064 4.805 1 5.952 1 7.318 1 8.785 2.23 10 3.781 10H6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H3.781C1.708 11 0 9.366 0 7.318c0-1.763 1.266-3.223 2.942-3.593.143-.863.698-1.723 1.464-2.383z"/>
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.646 4.146a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l3 3a.5.5 0 0 1-.708.708L8.5 5.707V14.5a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0V5.707L5.354 7.854a.5.5 0 1 1-.708-.708l3-3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h5 class="mt-3">일괄 업로드</h5>
        <p class="text-muted">여러 SVN 저장소를 한 번에 등록하고 마이그레이션</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="rounded-circle bg-success text-white d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-repeat" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M11.534 7h3.932a.25.25 0 0 1 .192.41l-1.966 2.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.384 0l-1.966-2.36a.25.25 0 0 1 .192-.41zm-11 2h3.932a.25.25 0 0 0 .192-.41L2.692 6.23a.25.25 0 0 0-.384 0L.342 8.59A.25.25 0 0 0 .534 9z"/>
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 3c-1.552 0-2.94.707-3.857 1.818a.5.5 0 1 1-.771-.636A6.002 6.002 0 0 1 13.917 7H12.9A5.002 5.002 0 0 0 8 3zM3.1 9a5.002 5.002 0 0 0 8.757 2.182.5.5 0 1 1 .771.636A6.002 6.002 0 0 1 2.083 9H3.1z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h5 class="mt-3">증분 동기화</h5>
        <p class="text-muted">최신 커밋만 동기화하여 다운타임 최소화</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="rounded-circle bg-info text-white d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-graph-up" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M0 0h1v15h15v1H0V0Zm14.817 3.113a.5.5 0 0 1 .07.704l-4.5 5.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.74.037L7.06 6.767l-3.656 5.027a.5.5 0 0 1-.808-.588l4-5.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .758-.06l2.609 2.61 4.15-5.073a.5.5 0 0 1 .704-.07Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h5 class="mt-3">실시간 모니터링</h5>
        <p class="text-muted">진행률과 로그를 실시간으로 확인</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center">
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to "저장소 관리", repositories_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg me-2" %>
        <%= link_to "마이그레이션 현황", "#", class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg" %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "시작하기", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg me-2" %>
        <%= link_to "로그인", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
